						Laissez-moi un message, je vous répondrez dans les meilleurs délais.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="row">
					<div class="col-md-6">
						<div class="info-block mt-3">
							<div class="icon mb-2">
								<i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i>
							</div>
							<div class="content-block">
								<h4>Adresse</h4>
								<p>FRANCE<br>3400 Montpellier</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="col-md-6">
						<div class="info-block mt-3">
							<div class="icon mb-2">
								<i class="fas fa-thumbs-up"></i>
							</div>
							<div class="content-block">
								<h4>Réseaux sociaux</h4>
								<ul class="list-unstyled">
								<li class="mb-1"><a class="hoverable-small" href="https://www.facebook.com/hldeveloppeurweb" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">facebook</a></li>
								<li class="mb-1"><a class="hoverable-small" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/hugues-leger-developpeur-web" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">linkedin</a></li>
